Gazprom Partner in Northgas May Sell 49% Stake, Vedomosti Says

-- B y   Y u l i y a   F e d o r i n o v a
-- 
2011-08-02T04:57:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-02/gazprom-partner-in-northgas-may-sell-49-stake-vedomosti-says.html
OAO Gazprom partner in ZAO Northgas,
Farkhad Akhmedov, may exercise his  put option  to sell 49 percent
of the venture to Gazprom, Vedomosti reported today, citing a
letter from Gazprom Deputy Chairman Valery Golubev.  Akhmetov may ask to buy his stake in the venture if Gazprom
decides to decrease Northgas’s concentrate processing in one of
Gazprom’s plants, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yuliya Fedorinova in Moscow at 
 yfedorinova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Viljoen at 
 jviljoen@bloomberg.net  